            {
              "mark": "A1",
              "note": "$\\log_a 18 = \\log_a 2 + 2\\log_a 3$"
            },
            {
              "mark": "A1",
              "note": "$\\log_a 18 = p + 2q$"
            }
          ],
          "answer": "$p + 2q$",
          "solution": "Write $18 = 2 \\cdot 3^2$ and use the log laws:$$\\log_a 18 = \\log_a 2 + \\log_a 3^2 = \\log_a 2 + 2\\log_a 3 = p + 2q.$$",
          "verify": [
            "Eq(2*3**2, 18)"
          ]
        }
      ]
